Probelm statement: In health care systems every record is done on paper, which causes a real chaos after a limit of descriptions. This problem can be solved by making every paperwork online, which will be good for the doctor as well as the patient. 
Scope of the project: This project can be used all over india making india digitalized. This basic model can be converted into app that can handel large data sets. By this government can also be benefited by knowing that in which area which disease has how many no. of cases.
Target Audience: This is a B2C project hence target is every human which is using health care systems.
High level Features: This is a over wide india plan making india digital and making india ready for a better future.
